{"tid":2348043,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［代po]有個傻人跌咗八達通","createTime":"2020-12-31T12:34:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-31T13:21:03.000Z","uid":143023,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"1b5cf73d483146201752cace8a39f113e68402d2","tid":2348043,"uid":143023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T12:34:02.000Z","msg":"嗰個就係我女朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n今日同佢搭由寶達開往金鐘601巴士，坐喺上排中段右邊，我哋搭到北角落車，去埋北角匯睇貓，走先發現唔見咗八達通<img src=\"/assets/faces/catxm/headache.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n佢個八達通套係呢隻青蛙，用咗好多年所以個公仔都甩甩地色<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Hh7AaS4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHh7AaS4.jpg&h=70a402f2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n麻煩各位巴打幫下手<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cae85e37a52b27d0f2dee4fa79bdde4164ce7803","tid":2348043,"uid":144014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T12:42:59.000Z","msg":"幫下手推"},{"pid":"fade93cd8d85a136b1034f46fb45bbbc03adea14","tid":2348043,"uid":319555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T12:56:11.000Z","msg":"幫手推下"},{"pid":"6c5201c84a30959de09d208a115f82dd1340d8cc","tid":2348043,"uid":1436,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T12:57:55.000Z","msg":"幫手下推"},{"pid":"cebc0ce47f6b7e54c23c4155bb3b09c8bc437afc","tid":2348043,"uid":250491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T13:20:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5796a02b060f7aa4c66ae1eee49c0ac76d09cf1","tid":2348043,"uid":250491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T13:21:03.000Z","msg":"Cut左八達通先啦 <br />\n取消自動增值<br />\n怕比人用晒錢"}]}